String Immutable class
Merits:
1. It is thread safe to be used in multi-threaded environment which means multiple threads can work with immutable string.
2. String constant pool (SCP) is possible as string is immutable class which is used by JVM to optimize memory management.
3. String is a popular data type used heavily with HashMap data structure because of its immutable characteristics.

Demerits:
1. Any modification on String will create a new object occupying heap memory.
